'''特別警備隊'''（Special Boarding Unit，簡稱：SBU）是[[日本海上自衛隊|日本海上自衛隊]]的[[特種部隊|特種部隊]]，創立於2001年3月27日，作為日本當局對1999年[[北韓|北韓]]間諜船入侵[[能登半島|能登半島]]的回應<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kazama-mys.com/j/e-int_sog.html|title=Special Operations Units and Intelligence Organizations in Japan|accessdate=2009-10-06|date=2004-04-19|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192518/http://kazama-mys.com/j/e-int_sog.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/25/world/japan-says-a-mystery-boat-fired-rockets-at-its-ships.html?pagewanted=2|title=Japan Says a Mystery Boat Fired Rockets at Its Ships|accessdate=2009-10-06|author=James Brooke|date=2001-12-25|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819134728/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/25/world/japan-says-a-mystery-boat-fired-rockets-at-its-ships.html?pagewanted=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該部隊以[[美國海軍|美國海軍]][[海豹部隊|海豹部隊]]和[[英國皇家海軍|英國皇家海軍]][[特別舟艇隊|特別舟艇隊]]為模範，架構更是以後者為標準。<ref name="Scandal"/><ref name="RR">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040603005534/http://www.renegaderecon.com/recon_details.php?id=138|url=http://www.renegaderecon.com/recon_details.php?id=138|title=The new Tokyo Marui AEG: MP5 Japanese Police/Military Version|date=2004-05-13|accessdate=2009-02-07|publisher=Renegade Recon|archivedate=2004-06-03 }}</ref>SBU的總部位於[[廣島縣|廣島縣]][[江田島市|江田島市]]。<ref name="MSDF SF">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CWsdwvBD?url=http://jieitaisaiyou.web.fc2.com/tokusyu_msdf.html|url= http://jieitaisaiyou.web.fc2.com/tokusyu_msdf.html|accessdate=2012-11-28|archivedate=2012-11-29|script-title=ja:海上自衛隊 特殊部隊 解説|language=ja}}</ref>

SBU的任務包括各種涉及海上反恐的作戰。<ref name="Death Report">{{cite web|url=http://www.mod.go.jp/j/press/sankou/report/houkoku.html|script-title=ja:「海上自衛隊特別警備隊関係の課程学生の死亡事案について」|accessdate=2010-04-22|publisher=[[Ministry_of_Defense_(Japan)|Japanese Ministry of Defense]]|language=ja|archive-date=2011-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110323210955/http://www.mod.go.jp/j/press/sankou/report/houkoku.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是其任務性質與[[海上保安廳|海上保安廳]]的[[特殊警備隊|特殊警備隊]]有所重疊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20040330a4.html|title=GSDF inaugurates undercover antiterrorist squad|author=Nao Shimoyachi|publisher=[[The_Japan_Times|The Japan Times]]|date=2004-03-30|accessdate=2009-02-07|archive-date=2011-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110820081017/http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20040330a4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

作為一支特種部隊，SBU對人員、訓練和武器等各方面都保持高度保密。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www8.cao.go.jp/jyouhou/tousin/h17-06/267.pdf|script-title=ja:「答申書 『大湊における寒冷地実習に関する特別警備隊一般命令』の一部開示決定に関する件」|accessdate=2009-02-07|language=ja|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182413/http://www8.cao.go.jp/jyouhou/tousin/h17-06/267.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在公眾場合活動時其隊員會佩戴[[巴拉克拉瓦頭套|巴拉克拉瓦頭套]]掩飾身份。<ref name="MSDF SF"/>

==歷史==
SBU是基於海上自衛隊未能有效阻止北韓間諜船入侵能登半島水域而於1999年創立。<ref name="Scandal"/><ref name="News">{{cite web|url=http://satellite.tmcnet.com/news/2009/01/21/3930380.htm|title=Special MSDF unit eyed to fight piracy|accessdate=2009-02-07|date=2009-01-21|publisher=Technology Marketing Corporation|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001445/http://satellite.tmcnet.com/news/2009/01/21/3930380.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Death Report"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/documents/organization/10965.pdf|title=DoS East Asia and Pacific Region, Japan, Exchange Training, FY 01|accessdate=2009-02-07|publisher=[[United_States_Department_of_State|State Department]]}}</ref>自成立後，該部隊在江田島市進行了非公開的秘密訓練，包括實習各種登船戰術。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chugoku-np.co.jp/abom/anpo/anpo0716.html|script-title=ja:装備も訓練も霧の中|language=ja|accessdate=2009-02-07|archive-date=2000-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20001119215200/http://www.chugoku-np.co.jp/abom/anpo/anpo0716.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>訓練終在2000年完成。<ref name="History">{{cite web |url=http://www5f.biglobe.ne.jp/~sbu/DATABASE-JAPAN.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060628015445/http://www5f.biglobe.ne.jp/~sbu/DATABASE-JAPAN.htm |archivedate=2006-06-28 |script-title=ja:日本国の精鋭部隊＆特殊部隊 |accessdate=2009-10-06 | language=ja}}</ref>SBU在2001年12月的[[奄美大島海戰|奄美大島海戰]]期間首次動員，但在部隊等待命令準備行動前目標船隻已遭擊沈。 <ref name="History"/><ref name="History"/>該部隊於2007年首次向公眾公開其訓練。<ref name="Public">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304193907/http://www.asagumo-news.com/graph/070705/070705G.html|url=http://www.asagumo-news.com/graph/070705/070705G.html|script-title=ja:特警隊広報展示高速ボートで不審船へ黒ずくめ武装隊員　素早く乗船、無力化|accessdate=2009-02-07|archivedate=2009-03-04|language=ja}}</ref><ref name="Chopper">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220082052/http://www.asagumo-news.com/news/200901/090122/09012204.html|url=http://www.asagumo-news.com/news/200901/090122/09012204.html|script-title=ja:どう取り組む　海賊対策＜中＞排除できない「交戦」　制約多い特警隊の派遣|accessdate=2009-02-07|archivedate=2012-02-20|language=ja}}</ref>

當SBU成立後，它嘗試邀請美國海軍[[海豹部隊|海豹部隊]]來為其隊員進行訓練，可是因對方太忙未能成事，故最後邀請了英國皇家海軍[[特別舟艇隊|特別舟艇隊]]進行訓練。<ref name="RR"/><ref name="History"/><ref name="MSDF SF"/>不過，SBU後來也有跟海豹部隊進行聯合訓練。<ref name="SAT Structure">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CEizHd5b?url=http://www.kjclub.com/jp/exchange/photo/read.php?tname=exc_board_53&uid=5386&fid=5386&thread=1000000&idx=1&page=1&number=4103|archivedate=2012-11-17|script-title=ja:日本の特殊部隊|url=http://www.kjclub.com/jp/exchange/photo/read.php?tname=exc_board_53&uid=5386&fid=5386&thread=1000000&idx=1&page=1&number=4103|language=ja}}</ref>

基於其危險及高度專業的任務性質，日本政府通過一項修正法案來增加SBU隊員的薪金。<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071010053612/http://www.shugiin.go.jp/itdb_housei.nsf/html/housei/h147058.htm|url=http://www.shugiin.go.jp/itdb_housei.nsf/html/housei/h147058.htm|script-title=ja:「防衛庁設置法等の一部を改正する法律」|accessdate=2009-02-07|language=ja|archivedate=2007-10-10 }}</ref>

目前已知，SBU會被部署到[[索馬里|索馬里]]執行反海盜任務。<ref name="News"/> <ref name="Deployment"/>

據指，SBU能夠在日本公民在外國被綁架時部署到海外與美軍特種作戰部隊一同執行營救行動。<ref name="MSDF SF"/>

SBU於2016年第42次G7峰會期間與警方的[[特殊急襲部隊|特殊急襲部隊]]一同擔任保安工作。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://biz-journal.jp/2016/06/post_15327_2.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2020-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522035427/https://biz-journal.jp/2016/06/post_15327_2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

